cargo-0.72.commit_message:
Bump cargo to 0.72

And undo all the pinning.

Revert "Explicitly build the rlib"

This reverts commit 596c582deed419b0cf1f80b9be77ff705df20e01.

Fixes #322.

Add a library.import_library configuration option

It is used to disable the generation of import_libraries when
unnecessary in platforms that need it to link libraries (e.g. Windows).
Workaround cargo not requiring windows-sys Console support
